-- American Alison Riske Upsets Seventh-Seeded Kvitova at U.S. Open
-- B y   M a s o n   L e v i n s o n
-- 2013-08-31T16:16:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-31/american-alison-riske-upsets-seventh-seeded-kvitova-at-u-s-open.html
American wild card Alison Riske
upset seventh-seeded Petra Kvitova of the Czech Republic 6-3,
6-0 at the U.S. Open in  New York , reaching the fourth round of a
Grand Slam tennis tournament for the first time in her career.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
